lopers and subject matter experts during the system design phase to ensure the system design meets the business needs. Responsible for creating and documenting requirements, process flows, use cases, field level specifications, business rules, etc. Conduct and facilitates Pre-RDW and RDW sessions. Also Facilitated bi-weekly scrum meeting and led the sprint planning meeting Review the test plan and test scenarios to ensure test coverage. Analyze the defects to determine the root cause and assign it appropriately for resolution. Support ad-hoc business analysis or assessments as requested. Tools and technologies: Guidewire Policy Center 8.0 OR 9.0, Guidewire Billing Center, Guidewire Portal 2.0, Atlassian JIRA, MS Excel, PowerPoint, Word, MS SharePoint. ", 
